thread.title: BRIEF-CASIN Guoxing Property Development sees FY 2017 net profit up 57.2 pct to 102.1 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-CASIN Guoxing Property Development sees FY 2017 net profit up 57.2 pct to 102.1 pct

organizations.name: casin guoxing property development co ltd

text:
Jan 31(Reuters) - CASIN Guoxing Property Development Co Ltd
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 57.2 percent to 102.1 percent, or to be 175 million yuan to 225 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 111.3 million yuan
* Says increased income from unit and tax preference are the main reasons for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/N9SMi3
